response.original_title: GCW Fight Club 2023, Night One - The Art of War Games
response.overview: On October 7th GCW: Fight Club 2023, Night One - The Art of War Games is live on FITE+ straight from Showboat Hotel in Atlantic City, NJ. The event features War Games match where Team Freedoms (Jun Kasai, Masashi Takeda, Takashi Sasaki, Toru Sugiura & Violento Jack) take on Team GCW (Ciclope, John Wayne Murdoch, Miedo Extremo, Nick Gage & Rina Yamashita).  Also in the lineup  Richard Holliday vs Charles Mason  Tony Deppen vs Alec Price  GCW World Title Match  Blake Christian (c) vs Jimmy Lloyd
